{"tid":377963,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解「聞」字會關嗅覺事？","createTime":"2017-08-28T06:21:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-28T06:44:10.000Z","uid":42369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e0ae10c5d958d56f60c0a63339bedeeedaf287f6","tid":377963,"uid":42369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T06:21:13.000Z","msg":"明明就係耳仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"614cb827d0291c9ebfe96dcde27100b145567ea4","tid":377963,"uid":135855,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T06:23:02.000Z","msg":"聞說"},{"pid":"a142e55c0a68ead5c6a2428bd30d535508f6748e","tid":377963,"uid":55614,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T06:23:56.000Z","msg":"𨳒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"729068e95b6f6191499be690561012d0f16aaeb0","tid":377963,"uid":51978,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T06:25:30.000Z","msg":"我地祖宗一早就知耳鼻喉相通"},{"pid":"5adde71ea572020e179d436b12b2f4332bb765e4","tid":377963,"uid":42369,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T06:27:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我地祖宗一早就知耳鼻喉相通</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n知聞也。从耳門聲。<br />\n清代 段玉裁《說文解字注》<br />\n往曰聽。來曰聞。大學曰。心不在焉。聽而不聞。引申之爲令聞廣譽。<br />\n<br />\n清朝都仲未有嗅覺既解釋喎<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.shuowen.org/view/7771\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.shuowen.org%2Fview%2F7771&d=cc5Vyip4F%2BDnLp4ljgfpGxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=f97204cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.shuowen.org/view/7771</a>"},{"pid":"fd54cde9331889a69c2b6143452cff32fe73624f","tid":377963,"uid":4780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T06:28:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聞說</blockquote><br />\n你時常在下午"},{"pid":"65a3c765ba6d3a2818f7e0771b8eed4ac02d6410","tid":377963,"uid":51978,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T06:28:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我地祖宗一早就知耳鼻喉相通</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n知聞也。从耳門聲。<br />\n清代 段玉裁《說文解字注》<br />\n往曰聽。來曰聞。大學曰。心不在焉。聽而不聞。引申之爲令聞廣譽。<br />\n<br />\n清朝都仲未有嗅覺既解釋喎<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.shuowen.org/view/7771\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.shuowen.org%2Fview%2F7771&d=cc5Vyip4F%2BDnLp4ljgfpGxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=f97204cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.shuowen.org/view/7771</a></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://dict.revised.moe.edu.tw/cgi-bin/cbdic/gsweb.cgi?o=dcbdic&amp;searchid=W00000011530\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdict.revised.moe.edu.tw%2Fcgi-bin%2Fcbdic%2Fgsweb.cgi%3Fo%3Ddcbdic%26searchid%3DW00000011530&d=cc5Vyip4F%2BDnLp4ljgfpGxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=3b996dc1\" target=\"_blank\">http://dict.revised.moe.edu.tw/cgi-bin/cbdic/gsweb.cgi?o=dcbdic&amp;searchid=W00000011530</a><br />\n<br />\n釋義 \t<br />\n[動]<br />\n1\t聽到。如：「百聞不如一見」。《論語．陽貨》：「子之武城，聞弦歌之聲。」《禮記．大學》：「心不在焉，視而不見，聽而不聞。」<br />\n2\t傳達、傳布。《詩經．小雅．鶴鳴》：「鶴鳴于九皋，聲聞于野。」《呂氏春秋．審應覽．重言》：「與仲父謀伐莒，謀未發而聞其國。」<br />\n3\t著稱。《隋書．卷七七．隱逸傳．李士謙傳》：「髫齓喪父，事母以孝聞。」唐．李白〈贈孟浩然〉詩：「吾愛孟夫子，風流天下聞。」<br />\n4\t<span style=\"color: red;\">用鼻子嗅。如：「入芝蘭之室，久而不聞其香。」《韓非子．十過》：「共王駕而自往，入其幄中，聞酒臭而還。」</span>"},{"pid":"91d5aea25eed7dfc5253d91c0278bf3f3cc6ccf5","tid":377963,"uid":34503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T06:29:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>聞說</blockquote><br />\n你時常在下午</blockquote><br />\n來這裡寄信片"},{"pid":"126e37cdaa1d40e9678e6fc23d87125e06fe3f3d","tid":377963,"uid":42369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T06:29:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我地祖宗一早就知耳鼻喉相通</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n知聞也。从耳門聲。<br />\n清代 段玉裁《說文解字注》<br />\n往曰聽。來曰聞。大學曰。心不在焉。聽而不聞。引申之爲令聞廣譽。<br />\n<br />\n清朝都仲未有嗅覺既解釋喎<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.shuowen.org/view/7771\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.shuowen.org%2Fview%2F7771&d=cc5Vyip4F%2BDnLp4ljgfpGxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU